DECLARE
  v_date      DATE;
  v_user      VARCHAR2(10);
  v_curr      VARCHAR2(5);
  
  v_sub_gl_acc    NUMBER;
  v_acc_gl_acc    NUMBER;
  v_usg_gl_acc    NUMBER;
  v_sub_cat     VARCHAR2(10);
  v_sub_code    VARCHAR2(10);
  v_sub_type    VARCHAR2(10);
  v_acc_cat     VARCHAR2(10);
  v_acc_code    VARCHAR2(10);
  v_acc_type    VARCHAR2(10);
  v_usg_cat     VARCHAR2(10);
  v_usg_code    VARCHAR2(10);
  v_usg_type    VARCHAR2(10);
  

  
 PROCEDURE  CREATE_RATEPLAN(
     p_des             VARCHAR2,
     p_shdes           VARCHAR2,
     p_srvcl           NUMBER,
     p_glb             VARCHAR2,
     p_curr            VARCHAR2,  
     p_date            DATE,
     p_user            VARCHAR2,
     p_pde_rateplan    VARCHAR2,
     p_pay_method_ind  VARCHAR2)
  
  IS
  v_tmcode    NUMBER;
  v_srvcl     NUMBER;
  v_so        NUMBER;
  v_curr      NUMBER;
  v_chg_code  NUMBER;
  v_rec_ver   NUMBER := 1;
  v_vscode    NUMBER := 0;
  v_status    VARCHAR2 (1) := 'W';
  
  BEGIN
  --SELECT NVL(MAX(TMCODE),0)+1 INTO v_tmcode FROM RATEPLAN;
  
   NEXTFREE.GETVALUE('MAX_TMCODE',v_tmcode);
  
  
  SELECT FC_ID INTO v_curr
  FROM FORCURR
  WHERE FCCODE = p_curr;
  
  IF ( p_srvcl IS NOT NULL )
  THEN
  
  SELECT SERVICE_CLASS_ID into v_srvcl from SERVICE_CLASS where EXTERNAL_KEY =p_srvcl;
  SELECT CHARGING_ENGINE_CODE INTO v_chg_code FROM CHARGING_ENGINE WHERE SHDES = 'CS';
 
  ELSE
  
    v_srvcl := NULL;
    
    SELECT CHARGING_ENGINE_CODE INTO v_chg_code FROM CHARGING_ENGINE WHERE SHDES = 'BSCS' ;
    
  END IF;
  
  
  
  
  INSERT INTO rateplan (tmcode,
                               des,
                               shdes,
                               tmglobal,
                               prerated_tap_rp_ind,
                               rec_version,
                               pde_rateplan,
                               charging_engine_code,
                               service_class_id,
                               payment_method_ind)
           VALUES   (v_tmcode,
                     p_des,
                     p_shdes,
                     p_glb,
                     'N',
                     v_rec_ver,
                     p_pde_rateplan,
                     v_chg_code,
                     v_srvcl,
                      p_pay_method_ind);
                      
                      
INSERT INTO rateplan_version (tmcode,
                              vscode,
                              vsdate,
                              status,
                              tmrc,
                              currency,
                              rec_version)
           VALUES   (v_tmcode,
                     v_vscode,
                     p_date,
                     v_status,
                     0,
                     v_curr,
                     v_rec_ver);
                     
UPDATE   rateplan
            SET   import_export_flag =
                     (import_export_flag + 2 - BITAND (import_export_flag, 2))
          WHERE   tmcode = v_tmcode;

         UPDATE   rateplan_version
            SET   import_export_flag =
                     (import_export_flag + 2 - BITAND (import_export_flag, 2))
          WHERE   tmcode = v_tmcode AND vscode = v_vscode;
          
END;

PROCEDURE ADD_TARIFF_SER_PACK (p_tmshdes          VARCHAR2,
                                  p_spshdes          VARCHAR2,
                                  p_ser_pack_def     VARCHAR2
                                  )
   IS
      v_tmcode     NUMBER;
      v_spcode     NUMBER;
      v_tmvscode   NUMBER := 0;
      
   BEGIN
      SELECT   tmcode
        INTO   v_tmcode
        FROM   rateplan
       WHERE   shdes = p_tmshdes;

      SELECT   spcode
        INTO   v_spcode
        FROM   mpusptab
       WHERE   shdes = p_spshdes;

     
         INSERT INTO tariff_service_package (tmcode,
                                             tmvscode,
                                             spcode,
                                             service_package_def,
                                             atomic_service_package)
           VALUES   (v_tmcode,
                     v_tmvscode,
                     v_spcode,
                     p_ser_pack_def,
                     NULL);
     
   END;
   
   PROCEDURE LNK_TM_TM1
( p_tm        VARCHAR2,
  p_sp        VARCHAR2,
  p_sn        VARCHAR2,
  p_pre       VARCHAR2,
  p_sub       NUMBER,
  p_acc       NUMBER,
  p_frq_ind   VARCHAR2,
  p_amt_ind   VARCHAR2,
  p_evt       NUMBER, 
  p_sub_gl_acc    NUMBER,
  p_acc_gl_acc    NUMBER,
  p_usg_gl_acc    NUMBER,
  p_sub_cat     VARCHAR2,
  p_sub_code    VARCHAR2,
  p_sub_type    VARCHAR2,
  p_acc_cat     VARCHAR2,
  p_acc_code    VARCHAR2,
  p_acc_type    VARCHAR2,
  p_usg_cat     VARCHAR2,
  p_usg_code    VARCHAR2,
  p_usg_type    VARCHAR2,
  p_date      DATE,
  p_user      VARCHAR2 )
IS
  v_tmcode    NUMBER;
  v_spcode    NUMBER;
  v_sncode    NUMBER;
  v_usg_pymt  NUMBER;
  v_sub_pymt  NUMBER;
  v_typ_ctrl  NUMBER;
  v_snind     VARCHAR2(1);
BEGIN
    
  SELECT TMCODE INTO v_tmcode
    FROM RATEPLAN
    WHERE SHDES = p_tm;
    
  SELECT SPCODE INTO v_spcode
    FROM MPUSPTAB
    WHERE SHDES = p_sp;
    
    SELECT   sncode
        INTO   v_sncode
        FROM   mpusntab
       WHERE   shdes = p_sn;

  SELECT NVL(SNIND,'P') into v_snind 
  FROM MPULKNXC
  WHERE SNCODE=v_sncode;
  
    IF (v_snind = 'U' )
    THEN
  
      IF ( p_pre = 'X' )
      THEN
  
        v_usg_pymt := 2;
        v_sub_pymt := 1;
        v_typ_ctrl := 1;
    
      ELSE
  
        v_usg_pymt := 1;
        v_sub_pymt := 1;
        v_typ_ctrl := 2;
    
      END IF;

      INSERT INTO MPULKTM1
        ( TMCODE, VSCODE, VSDATE, STATUS, SPCODE, SNCODE,SUBSCRIPT, ACCESSFEE,EVENT,SRVIND,ECHIND,FRQIND,PROIND, ADVIND,SUSIND,
        PRINTSUBSCRIND, PRINTACCESSIND,INITIAL_CREDIT,DEPOSIT,INTERVAL_TYPE,INTERVAL,BOP_MODE_ID,OVW_RECUR_AMOUNT,
        OVW_PERIOD_TYPE,OVW_PERIOD_LENGTH,CHARGING_SCHEDULE,AMTIND,SUB_GL_ACC_PACK_ID,ACC_GL_ACC_PACK_ID,USG_GL_ACC_PACK_ID,
        SUBSERV_CATCODE,SUBSERV_CODE,SUBSERV_TYPE,ACCSERV_CATCODE,ACCSERV_CODE,ACCSERV_TYPE,USGSERV_CATCODE,USGSERV_CODE,
        USGSERV_TYPE,GL_PACK_SYSTEM_SCENARIO_FLAG,NON_EXPL_SERV_PREPAID_IND,SERVICE_PRIORITY,DEF_PAYMENT_COND_USG,REC_VERSION,
        PAYMENT_COND_CHANGEABLE_USG,DEF_TIME_PACKAGE_USG,DEF_PAYMENT_COND_ONETIME_REC,DEF_TYPE_OF_CONTROL,PRM_PRINT_IND)
        VALUES
        (v_tmcode,0,p_date,'W',v_spcode,v_sncode,p_sub,p_acc,p_evt,'P',NULL,p_frq_ind,'Y','P','N','N','N',NULL,NULL,'M',1,
        NULL,NULL,'M',NULL,'B',p_amt_ind,p_sub_gl_acc,p_acc_gl_acc,p_usg_gl_acc,p_sub_cat,p_sub_code,p_sub_type,
        p_acc_cat,p_acc_code,p_acc_type,p_usg_cat,p_usg_code,p_usg_type,NULL,p_pre,0,v_usg_pymt,1,NULL,NULL,v_sub_pymt,v_typ_ctrl,'N');
    END IF;
    
    IF ( v_snind = 'E'  )
    THEN
    
      v_usg_pymt := 3;
      v_sub_pymt := 1;
      v_typ_ctrl := NULL;
                
    INSERT INTO MPULKTM1
        ( TMCODE, VSCODE, VSDATE, STATUS, SPCODE, SNCODE,SUBSCRIPT, ACCESSFEE,EVENT,SRVIND,ECHIND,FRQIND,PROIND, ADVIND,SUSIND,
        PRINTSUBSCRIND, PRINTACCESSIND,INITIAL_CREDIT,DEPOSIT,INTERVAL_TYPE,INTERVAL,BOP_MODE_ID,OVW_RECUR_AMOUNT,
        OVW_PERIOD_TYPE,OVW_PERIOD_LENGTH,CHARGING_SCHEDULE,AMTIND,SUB_GL_ACC_PACK_ID,ACC_GL_ACC_PACK_ID,USG_GL_ACC_PACK_ID,
        SUBSERV_CATCODE,SUBSERV_CODE,SUBSERV_TYPE,ACCSERV_CATCODE,ACCSERV_CODE,ACCSERV_TYPE,USGSERV_CATCODE,
        USGSERV_CODE,USGSERV_TYPE,GL_PACK_SYSTEM_SCENARIO_FLAG,NON_EXPL_SERV_PREPAID_IND,SERVICE_PRIORITY,DEF_PAYMENT_COND_USG,
        REC_VERSION,PAYMENT_COND_CHANGEABLE_USG,DEF_TIME_PACKAGE_USG,DEF_PAYMENT_COND_ONETIME_REC,DEF_TYPE_OF_CONTROL,PRM_PRINT_IND)
        VALUES
        (v_tmcode,0,p_date,'W',v_spcode,v_sncode,p_sub,p_acc,p_evt,'P',NULL,p_frq_ind,'Y','P','N','N','N',0,NULL,'M',1,
        NULL,NULL,'M',NULL,'B',p_amt_ind,p_sub_gl_acc,p_acc_gl_acc,p_usg_gl_acc,p_sub_cat,p_sub_code,p_sub_type,
        p_acc_cat,p_acc_code,p_acc_type,p_usg_cat,p_usg_code,p_usg_type,NULL,p_pre,0,v_usg_pymt,1,NULL,NULL,v_sub_pymt,v_typ_ctrl,'N');
        
    END IF;
        
        IF ( v_snind = 'A' )
    THEN
    
      v_usg_pymt := 1;
      v_sub_pymt := NULL;
      v_typ_ctrl := NULL;
      
      
          
    INSERT INTO MPULKTM1 (TMCODE,VSCODE,VSDATE,STATUS,SPCODE,SNCODE,SUBSCRIPT,ACCESSFEE,EVENT,SRVIND,ECHIND,FRQIND,PROIND,ADVIND,SUSIND,
    PRINTSUBSCRIND,PRINTACCESSIND,INITIAL_CREDIT,DEPOSIT,INTERVAL_TYPE,INTERVAL,BOP_MODE_ID,OVW_RECUR_AMOUNT,OVW_PERIOD_TYPE,
    OVW_PERIOD_LENGTH,CHARGING_SCHEDULE,AMTIND,SUB_GL_ACC_PACK_ID,ACC_GL_ACC_PACK_ID,
    USG_GL_ACC_PACK_ID,SUBSERV_CATCODE,SUBSERV_CODE,SUBSERV_TYPE,ACCSERV_CATCODE,ACCSERV_CODE,ACCSERV_TYPE,USGSERV_CATCODE,
    USGSERV_CODE,USGSERV_TYPE,GL_PACK_SYSTEM_SCENARIO_FLAG,NON_EXPL_SERV_PREPAID_IND,SERVICE_PRIORITY,DEF_PAYMENT_COND_USG,
    REC_VERSION,PAYMENT_COND_CHANGEABLE_USG,DEF_TIME_PACKAGE_USG,DEF_PAYMENT_COND_ONETIME_REC,DEF_TYPE_OF_CONTROL,PRM_PRINT_IND)
  VALUES   
  (v_tmcode,0,p_date,'W',v_spcode,v_sncode,p_sub,p_acc,p_evt,'E',v_snind,p_frq_ind,NULL,NULL,NULL,'N','N',NULL,NULL,'M', 1, NULL, NULL,
   NULL,NULL,'B',p_amt_ind,p_sub_gl_acc,p_acc_gl_acc,p_usg_gl_acc,p_sub_cat,p_sub_code,
   p_sub_type,p_acc_cat,p_acc_code,p_acc_type,p_usg_cat,p_usg_code,p_usg_type,NULL,p_pre,0,v_usg_pymt, 1, NULL,NULL,v_sub_pymt, v_typ_ctrl,'N');
    
    END IF;
  
    IF ( v_snind = 'R')
    THEN
    
      v_usg_pymt := 1;
      v_sub_pymt := NULL;
      v_typ_ctrl := NULL;
      
      
          
    INSERT INTO MPULKTM1 
    (TMCODE,VSCODE,VSDATE,STATUS,SPCODE,SNCODE,SUBSCRIPT,ACCESSFEE,EVENT,SRVIND,ECHIND,FRQIND,PROIND,ADVIND,
     SUSIND,PRINTSUBSCRIND,PRINTACCESSIND,INITIAL_CREDIT,DEPOSIT,INTERVAL_TYPE,INTERVAL,BOP_MODE_ID,OVW_RECUR_AMOUNT,
     OVW_PERIOD_TYPE,OVW_PERIOD_LENGTH,CHARGING_SCHEDULE,AMTIND,SUB_GL_ACC_PACK_ID,
     ACC_GL_ACC_PACK_ID,USG_GL_ACC_PACK_ID,SUBSERV_CATCODE,SUBSERV_CODE,SUBSERV_TYPE,ACCSERV_CATCODE,ACCSERV_CODE,ACCSERV_TYPE,
     USGSERV_CATCODE,USGSERV_CODE,USGSERV_TYPE,GL_PACK_SYSTEM_SCENARIO_FLAG,NON_EXPL_SERV_PREPAID_IND,SERVICE_PRIORITY,DEF_PAYMENT_COND_USG,
     REC_VERSION,PAYMENT_COND_CHANGEABLE_USG,DEF_TIME_PACKAGE_USG,DEF_PAYMENT_COND_ONETIME_REC,DEF_TYPE_OF_CONTROL,PRM_PRINT_IND)
  VALUES   
  (v_tmcode,0,p_date,'W',v_spcode,v_sncode,p_sub,p_acc,DECODE(p_pre, 'X', 0, p_evt),'E',DECODE(p_pre, 'X', 'A',v_snind),p_frq_ind,NULL,NULL,NULL,
  'N','N',NULL,NULL,'M', 1, NULL, NULL,NULL,NULL,'B',p_amt_ind,p_sub_gl_acc,p_acc_gl_acc,p_usg_gl_acc,p_sub_cat,p_sub_code,
   p_sub_type,p_acc_cat,p_acc_code,p_acc_type,p_usg_cat,p_usg_code,p_usg_type,NULL,p_pre,0,v_usg_pymt, 1, NULL,NULL,v_sub_pymt, v_typ_ctrl,'N');
    
    END IF;
    
    IF ( v_snind IN ( 'V' ) )
    THEN
    
      v_usg_pymt := 1;
      v_sub_pymt := NULL;
      v_typ_ctrl := NULL;
      
          
    INSERT INTO MPULKTM1 
    (TMCODE,VSCODE,VSDATE,STATUS,SPCODE,SNCODE,SUBSCRIPT,ACCESSFEE,EVENT,SRVIND,ECHIND,FRQIND,PROIND,ADVIND,
    SUSIND,PRINTSUBSCRIND,PRINTACCESSIND,INITIAL_CREDIT,DEPOSIT,INTERVAL_TYPE,INTERVAL,BOP_MODE_ID,OVW_RECUR_AMOUNT,
    OVW_PERIOD_TYPE,OVW_PERIOD_LENGTH,CHARGING_SCHEDULE,AMTIND,SUB_GL_ACC_PACK_ID,
    ACC_GL_ACC_PACK_ID,USG_GL_ACC_PACK_ID,SUBSERV_CATCODE,SUBSERV_CODE,SUBSERV_TYPE,ACCSERV_CATCODE,ACCSERV_CODE,ACCSERV_TYPE,
    USGSERV_CATCODE,USGSERV_CODE,USGSERV_TYPE,GL_PACK_SYSTEM_SCENARIO_FLAG,NON_EXPL_SERV_PREPAID_IND,SERVICE_PRIORITY,DEF_PAYMENT_COND_USG,
    REC_VERSION,PAYMENT_COND_CHANGEABLE_USG,DEF_TIME_PACKAGE_USG,DEF_PAYMENT_COND_ONETIME_REC,DEF_TYPE_OF_CONTROL,PRM_PRINT_IND)
    VALUES   
    (v_tmcode,0,p_date,'W',v_spcode,v_sncode,p_sub,p_acc,p_evt,'P',NULL,p_frq_ind,'Y','P','N','N','N',NULL,NULL,'M', 1,
    NULL, NULL,NULL,NULL,'B',p_amt_ind,p_sub_gl_acc,p_acc_gl_acc,p_usg_gl_acc,p_sub_cat,p_sub_code,p_sub_type,p_acc_cat,p_acc_code,
    p_acc_type,p_usg_cat,p_usg_code,p_usg_type,NULL,p_pre,0,v_usg_pymt, 1, NULL,NULL,v_sub_pymt, v_typ_ctrl,'N');
    
    END IF; 
    IF (v_snind IN ( 'P' ))
    THEN
    
      v_usg_pymt := 3;
      v_sub_pymt := NULL;
      v_typ_ctrl := NULL;
      
          
    INSERT INTO MPULKTM1 
    (TMCODE,VSCODE,VSDATE,STATUS,SPCODE,SNCODE,SUBSCRIPT,ACCESSFEE,EVENT,SRVIND,ECHIND,FRQIND,PROIND,ADVIND,
    SUSIND,PRINTSUBSCRIND,PRINTACCESSIND,INITIAL_CREDIT,DEPOSIT,INTERVAL_TYPE,INTERVAL,BOP_MODE_ID,OVW_RECUR_AMOUNT,
    OVW_PERIOD_TYPE,OVW_PERIOD_LENGTH,CHARGING_SCHEDULE,AMTIND,SUB_GL_ACC_PACK_ID,
    ACC_GL_ACC_PACK_ID,USG_GL_ACC_PACK_ID,SUBSERV_CATCODE,SUBSERV_CODE,SUBSERV_TYPE,ACCSERV_CATCODE,ACCSERV_CODE,ACCSERV_TYPE,
    USGSERV_CATCODE,USGSERV_CODE,USGSERV_TYPE,GL_PACK_SYSTEM_SCENARIO_FLAG,NON_EXPL_SERV_PREPAID_IND,SERVICE_PRIORITY,DEF_PAYMENT_COND_USG,
    REC_VERSION,PAYMENT_COND_CHANGEABLE_USG,DEF_TIME_PACKAGE_USG,DEF_PAYMENT_COND_ONETIME_REC,DEF_TYPE_OF_CONTROL,PRM_PRINT_IND)
    VALUES   
    (v_tmcode,0,p_date,'W',v_spcode,v_sncode,p_sub,p_acc,p_evt,'P',NULL,p_frq_ind,'Y','P','N','N','N',NULL,NULL,'M', 1,
    NULL, NULL,NULL,NULL,'B',p_amt_ind,p_sub_gl_acc,p_acc_gl_acc,p_usg_gl_acc,p_sub_cat,p_sub_code,p_sub_type,p_acc_cat,p_acc_code,
    p_acc_type,p_usg_cat,p_usg_code,p_usg_type,NULL,p_pre,0,v_usg_pymt, 1, NULL,NULL,v_sub_pymt, v_typ_ctrl,'N');
    
    END IF; 
    
    
    
    END;
    PROCEDURE LNK_TM_TM2
( p_tm        VARCHAR2,
  p_sp        VARCHAR2,
  p_sn        VARCHAR2,
  p_up        VARCHAR2,
  p_ri        VARCHAR2,
  p_usgid     VARCHAR2,
  p_date      DATE,
  p_user      VARCHAR2
  )
IS
  v_tmcode    NUMBER;
  v_spcode    NUMBER;
  v_sncode    NUMBER;
  v_svlcode   VARCHAR2(20);
  v_upcode    NUMBER;
  v_ricode    NUMBER;
  v_usgid    NUMBER;
BEGIN
    
  SELECT TMCODE INTO v_tmcode
    FROM RATEPLAN
    WHERE SHDES = p_tm;
    
  SELECT SPCODE INTO v_spcode
    FROM MPUSPTAB
    WHERE SHDES = p_sp;

  SELECT UPCODE INTO v_upcode
    FROM MPUUPTAB
    WHERE SHDES = p_up;
    
  SELECT RICODE INTO v_ricode
    FROM MPURITAB
    WHERE SHDES = p_ri;
  
  SELECT SNCODE INTO v_sncode
    FROM MPUSNTAB
    WHERE SHDES = p_sn;
  
  SELECT USAGE_TYPE_ID INTO v_usgid
    FROM UDC_USAGE_TYPE_TABLE
    WHERE USAGE_TYPE_SHNAME = p_usgid;
        
  SELECT SVLCODE INTO v_svlcode
    FROM MPULKNXV
    WHERE SNCODE = v_sncode;

  INSERT INTO MPULKTM2
    ( TMCODE, VSCODE, VSDATE, STATUS, SPCODE, SNCODE, SVLCODE, RATEIND, UPCODE, RICODE,CP_PRICELIST_ID,REC_VERSION, USAGE_TYPE_ID )
    VALUES
    ( v_tmcode, 0, p_date, 'W', v_spcode, v_sncode, v_svlcode,'Y', v_upcode, v_ricode,NULL, 1, v_usgid );
 
END;
PROCEDURE SET_CORE
( p_tm        VARCHAR2,
  p_sp        VARCHAR2,
  p_sn        VARCHAR2,
  p_clshdes   VARCHAR2  )
IS
  v_tmcode    NUMBER;
  v_spcode    NUMBER;
  v_sncode    NUMBER;
  v_clcode    NUMBER;
BEGIN

  SELECT TMCODE INTO v_tmcode
    FROM RATEPLAN
    WHERE SHDES = p_tm;

  SELECT SPCODE INTO v_spcode
    FROM MPUSPTAB
    WHERE SHDES = p_sp;
    
  SELECT SNCODE INTO v_sncode
    FROM MPUSNTAB
    WHERE SHDES = p_sn;
    
    SELECT CLCODE INTO v_clcode
    FROM MPDCLTAB
    WHERE SHDES = p_clshdes;
    
  UPDATE MPULKTM1
    SET CSIND = 'X',
        CLCODE = v_clcode
    WHERE TMCODE = v_tmcode
    AND SPCODE = v_spcode
    AND SNCODE = v_sncode;
END;
PROCEDURE ADD_PARAM_TO_RP (p_tm_shdes    VARCHAR2,
                              p_sp_shdes    VARCHAR2,
                              p_sn_shdes    VARCHAR2)
   IS
      v_tmcode        NUMBER;
      v_spcode        NUMBER;
      v_sncode        NUMBER;
      v_pv_combi_id   NUMBER;
   BEGIN
      SELECT   NVL (MAX (PV_COMBI_ID), 0) + 1 INTO v_pv_combi_id FROM MPUPVTAB;

      SELECT   tmcode
        INTO   v_tmcode
        FROM   RATEPLAN
       WHERE   shdes = p_tm_shdes;

      SELECT   spcode
        INTO   v_spcode
        FROM   MPUSPTAB
       WHERE   shdes = p_sp_shdes;

      SELECT   sncode
        INTO   v_sncode
        FROM   MPUSNTAB
       WHERE   shdes = p_sn_shdes;

      INSERT INTO MPUPVTAB (PV_COMBI_ID)
        VALUES   (v_pv_combi_id);

      UPDATE   MPULKTM1
         SET   PV_COMBI_ID = v_pv_combi_id
       WHERE   TMCODE = v_tmcode AND SPCODE = v_spcode AND SNCODE = v_sncode;
   END;

   PROCEDURE INSERT_PARAM_PRICES (p_tm_shdes         VARCHAR2,
                                  p_sp_shdes         VARCHAR2,
                                  p_sn_shdes         VARCHAR2,
                                  p_prm_shdes        VARCHAR2,
                                  p_prm_print_ind    VARCHAR2,
                                  p_prm_value_des    VARCHAR2,
                                  p_set_id           NUMBER,
                                  p_sub_fees         FLOAT,
                                  p_acc_fees         FLOAT,
                                  p_lower_thres      NUMBER)
   IS
      v_tmcode        NUMBER;
      v_spcode        NUMBER;
      v_sncode        NUMBER;
      v_prm_id        NUMBER;
      v_pv_combi_id   NUMBER;
   BEGIN
      SELECT   tmcode
        INTO   v_tmcode
        FROM   RATEPLAN
       WHERE   shdes = p_tm_shdes;

      SELECT   spcode
        INTO   v_spcode
        FROM   MPUSPTAB
       WHERE   shdes = p_sp_shdes;

      SELECT   sncode
        INTO   v_sncode
        FROM   MPUSNTAB
       WHERE   shdes = p_sn_shdes;

      SELECT   parameter_id
        INTO   v_prm_id
        FROM   MKT_PARAMETER
       WHERE   shdes = p_prm_shdes;

      SELECT   pv_combi_id
        INTO   v_pv_combi_id
        FROM   MPULKTM1
       WHERE   TMCODE = v_tmcode AND SPCODE = v_spcode AND SNCODE = v_sncode;

      UPDATE   MPULKTM1
         SET   PRM_PRINT_IND = p_prm_print_ind
       WHERE   TMCODE = v_tmcode AND SPCODE = v_spcode AND SNCODE = v_sncode;

      INSERT INTO MPULKPV1 (PV_COMBI_ID,
                            VSCODE,
                            SET_ID,
                            DES,
                            SUBSCRIPT,
                            ACCESSFEE,
                            REC_VERSION)
        VALUES   (v_pv_combi_id,
                  0,
                  p_set_id,
                  p_prm_value_des,
                  p_sub_fees,
                  p_acc_fees,
                  1);

      INSERT INTO MPULKPV2 (PV_COMBI_ID,
                            VSCODE,
                            SET_ID,
                            SCCODE,
                            PARAMETER_ID,
                            LOWER_THRESHOLD,
                            PRM_VALUE_DATE,
                            PRM_VALUE_NUMBER,
                            PRM_VALUE_STRING,
                            REC_VERSION)
         SELECT   v_pv_combi_id,
                  0,
                  p_set_id,
                  1,
                  v_prm_id,
                  p_lower_thres,
                  PRM_VALUE_DATE,
                  PRM_VALUE_NUMBER,
                  PRM_VALUE_STRING,
                  1
           FROM   MKT_PARAMETER_DOMAIN
          WHERE   PARAMETER_ID = v_prm_id AND PRM_VALUE_DES = p_prm_value_des;
   END;   
PROCEDURE RELEASE_RATE_PLAN (p_tmshdes              VARCHAR2,
                             p_curr            VARCHAR2,
                             p_date                  DATE)
   IS
      v_vscode          NUMBER := 1;
      v_status          VARCHAR2 (1) := 'P';
      v_currency        NUMBER;
      v_tmcode          NUMBER;
      v_rec_ver         NUMBER := 1;
      v_rate_plan_ver   NUMBER;
      v_tmvscode        NUMBER := 1;
   BEGIN
  SELECT FC_ID INTO v_currency
  FROM FORCURR
  WHERE FCCODE = p_curr;

      SELECT   tmcode
        INTO   v_tmcode
        FROM   rateplan
       WHERE   shdes = p_tmshdes;
       
      FOR CUR_PRM IN (SELECT   PV_COMBI_ID
                        FROM   MPULKTM1
                       WHERE   TMCODE = v_tmcode AND PV_COMBI_ID IS NOT NULL)
      LOOP
         IF (CUR_PRM.PV_COMBI_ID IS NOT NULL)
         THEN
            INSERT INTO MPULKPVB (PV_COMBI_ID,
                                  VSCODE,
                                  SET_ID,
                                  DES,
                                  SUBSCRIPT,
                                  ACCESSFEE,
                                  REC_VERSION)
               SELECT   PV_COMBI_ID,
                        1,
                        SET_ID,
                        DES,
                        SUBSCRIPT,
                        ACCESSFEE,
                        REC_VERSION
                 FROM   MPULKPV1
                WHERE   PV_COMBI_ID = CUR_PRM.PV_COMBI_ID;

            INSERT INTO MPULKPVM (PV_COMBI_ID,
                                  VSCODE,
                                  SET_ID,
                                  SCCODE,
                                  PARAMETER_ID,
                                  LOWER_THRESHOLD,
                                  PRM_VALUE_DATE,
                                  PRM_VALUE_NUMBER,
                                  PRM_VALUE_STRING,
                                  REC_VERSION)
               SELECT   PV_COMBI_ID,
                        1,
                        SET_ID,
                        SCCODE,
                        PARAMETER_ID,
                        LOWER_THRESHOLD,
                        PRM_VALUE_DATE,
                        PRM_VALUE_NUMBER,
                        PRM_VALUE_STRING,
                        REC_VERSION
                 FROM   MPULKPV2
                WHERE   PV_COMBI_ID = CUR_PRM.PV_COMBI_ID;
         END IF;
      END LOOP;
                        

      INSERT INTO rateplan_version (tmcode,
                                    vscode,
                                    vsdate,
                                    status,
                                    tmrc,
                                    currency,
                                    rec_version,
                                    apdate
                                    )
        VALUES   (v_tmcode,
                  v_vscode,
                  p_date,
                  v_status,
                  0,
                  v_currency,
                  v_rec_ver,
                  p_date
                  );

      INSERT INTO mpulktmm (tmcode,
                            vscode,
                            vsdate,
                            status,
                            spcode,
                            sncode,
                            svlcode,
                            usage_type_id,
                            rateind,
                            upcode,
                            ricode,
                            cp_pricelist_id,
                            fallback_srv_flag,
                            rec_version)
         SELECT   tmcode,
                  v_vscode,
                  p_date,
                  v_status,
                  spcode,
                  sncode,
                  svlcode,
                  usage_type_id,
                  rateind,
                  upcode,
                  ricode,
                  cp_pricelist_id,
                  fallback_srv_flag,
                  1
           FROM   mpulktm2
          WHERE   tmcode = v_tmcode
                  AND (ricode IS NOT NULL OR cp_pricelist_id IS NOT NULL);

      INSERT INTO mpulktmb (tmcode,
                            vscode,
                            vsdate,
                            status,
                            spcode,
                            sncode,
                            srvind,
                            echind,
                            amtind,
                            frqind,
                            subscript,
                            accessfee,
                            event,
                            proind,
                            advind,
                            susind,
                            initial_credit,
                            subserv_catcode,
                            subserv_code,
                            subserv_type,
                            accserv_catcode,
                            accserv_code,
                            accserv_type,
                            usgserv_catcode,
                            usgserv_code,
                            usgserv_type,
                            csind,
                            clcode,
                            deposit,
                            interval_type,
                            INTERVAL,
                            pv_combi_id,
                            prm_print_ind,
                            printsubscrind,
                            printaccessind,
                            non_expl_serv_prepaid_ind,
                            bop_mode_id,
                            def_payment_cond_usg,
                            payment_cond_changeable_usg,
                            def_time_package_usg,
                            rec_version,
                            def_payment_cond_onetime_rec,
                            ovw_recur_amount,
                            ovw_period_type,
                            ovw_period_length,
                            def_type_of_control,
                            service_priority,
                            charging_schedule,
                            account_id,
                            sub_gl_acc_pack_id,
                            acc_gl_acc_pack_id,
                            usg_gl_acc_pack_id,
                            gl_pack_system_scenario_flag,
                            offer_id,
                            pam_config_id_rec_charge,
                            pam_config_id_main)
         SELECT   tmcode,
                  v_vscode,
                  p_date,
                  v_status,
                  spcode,
                  sncode,
                  srvind,
                  echind,
                  amtind,
                  frqind,
                  subscript,
                  accessfee,
                  event,
                  proind,
                  advind,
                  susind,
                  initial_credit,
                  subserv_catcode,
                  subserv_code,
                  subserv_type,
                  accserv_catcode,
                  accserv_code,
                  accserv_type,
                  usgserv_catcode,
                  usgserv_code,
                  usgserv_type,
                  csind,
                  clcode,
                  deposit,
                  interval_type,
                  INTERVAL,
                  pv_combi_id,
                  prm_print_ind,
                  printsubscrind,
                  printaccessind,
                  non_expl_serv_prepaid_ind,
                  bop_mode_id,
                  def_payment_cond_usg,
                  payment_cond_changeable_usg,
                  def_time_package_usg,
                  1,
                  def_payment_cond_onetime_rec,
                  ovw_recur_amount,
                  ovw_period_type,
                  ovw_period_length,
                  def_type_of_control,
                  service_priority,
                  charging_schedule,
                  account_id,
                  sub_gl_acc_pack_id,
                  acc_gl_acc_pack_id,
                  usg_gl_acc_pack_id,
                  gl_pack_system_scenario_flag,
                  offer_id,
                  pam_config_id_rec_charge,
                  pam_config_id_main
           FROM   mpulktm1
          WHERE   tmcode = v_tmcode;

      INSERT INTO tariff_service_package (tmcode,
                                          tmvscode,
                                          spcode,
                                          service_package_def,
                                          atomic_service_package)
         SELECT   tmcode,
                  v_tmvscode,
                  spcode,
                  service_package_def,
                  atomic_service_package
           FROM   tariff_service_package
          WHERE   tmcode = v_tmcode AND tmvscode = 0;

      INSERT INTO ratetyp_ratepln_service_srvpck (tmcode,
                                                  vscode,
                                                  spcode,
                                                  sncode,
                                                  rate_type_id)
         SELECT   tmcode,
                  v_vscode,
                  spcode,
                  sncode,
                  rate_type_id
           FROM   ratetyp_ratepln_service_srvpck
          WHERE   tmcode = v_tmcode AND vscode = 0;

      UPDATE   rateplan
         SET   import_export_flag =
                  (import_export_flag + 2 - BITAND (import_export_flag, 2))
       WHERE   tmcode = v_tmcode;

      SELECT   rec_version + 1
        INTO   v_rate_plan_ver
        FROM   rateplan_version
       WHERE   tmcode = v_tmcode AND vscode = v_vscode;

      UPDATE   rateplan_version
         SET   import_export_flag =
                  (import_export_flag + 2 - BITAND (import_export_flag, 2))
       WHERE   tmcode = v_tmcode AND vscode = v_vscode;

      UPDATE   rateplan_version
         SET   tmrc = 0,
               apdate = p_date,
               rec_version = v_rate_plan_ver
       WHERE   tmcode = v_tmcode AND vscode = 0;
   
   END;
    PROCEDURE LNK_PROFILE_RATEPLN(rp_shdes VARCHAR2,lc_description VARCHAR2,p_date DATE)
IS
v_tmcode NUMBER;
v_lc_id  NUMBER;
v_vscode NUMBER;

BEGIN
SELECT TMCODE into v_tmcode from RATEPLAN where shdes = rp_shdes;



SELECT   MAX (VSCODE) into v_vscode
  FROM   RATEPLAN_VERSION
 WHERE   TMCODE = v_tmcode AND STATUS = 'P';


SELECT   PREPAID_LC_PROFILE_ID
  INTO   v_lc_id
  FROM   PREPAID_LC_PROFILE
 WHERE   DESCRIPTION = lc_description;



INSERT INTO RATEPLAN_LNK_PPLC_PROFILE (TMCODE,
                                       PREPAID_LC_PROFILE_ID,
                                       REC_VERSION,
                                       VALID_FROM,
                                       VSCODE)
  VALUES   (v_tmcode,
            v_lc_id,
            1,
            p_date,
            v_vscode);

END;
PROCEDURE ASSIGN_BUSS_UNIT (p_shdes VARCHAR2, p_buss_unit VARCHAR2)
   IS
      v_rec_ver   NUMBER := 1;
      v_tmcode    NUMBER;
      v_bus_id    NUMBER;
      
  BEGIN
      SELECT   tmcode
        INTO   v_tmcode
        FROM   rateplan
       WHERE   shdes = p_shdes;
       
        SELECT   business_unit_id
        INTO   v_bus_id
        FROM   business_unit
       WHERE   business_unit_shdes = p_buss_unit;


      INSERT INTO rateplan_busunit (tmcode,business_unit_id,rec_version)
      VALUES   (v_tmcode,v_bus_id,v_rec_ver);
     
   END;
   PROCEDURE  LNK_PRICEGROUP_TM(p_shdes VARCHAR2,p_prg VARCHAR2)
   
   IS
   v_tmcode NUMBER;
   v_nxg_id NUMBER;
   BEGIN
   SELECT TMCODE into v_tmcode from RATEPLAN where shdes = p_shdes;
   
    SELECT   NVL (MAX (MPULKNXG_ID), 0) + 1
        INTO   v_nxg_id
        FROM   MPULKNXG;
   
   INSERT INTO MPULKNXG(TMCODE,PRGCODE,MPULKNXG_ID)
   VALUES
   (v_tmcode,p_prg,v_nxg_id);
   
   END;
 PROCEDURE LNK_PAM_CLASS_TM
( p_tm        VARCHAR2,
  p_sp        VARCHAR2,
  p_sn        VARCHAR2,
  p_cl_id   VARCHAR2  )
IS
  v_tmcode    NUMBER;
  v_spcode    NUMBER;
  v_sncode    NUMBER;
  v_cn_id   NUMBER;
BEGIN

  SELECT TMCODE INTO v_tmcode
    FROM RATEPLAN
    WHERE SHDES = p_tm;

  SELECT SPCODE INTO v_spcode
    FROM MPUSPTAB
    WHERE SHDES = p_sp;
    
  SELECT SNCODE INTO v_sncode
    FROM MPUSNTAB
    WHERE SHDES = p_sn;
    
    SELECT PAM_CONFIG_ID INTO v_cn_id
    FROM PAM_CONFIGURATION
    WHERE PAM_CLASS_ID =(SELECT PAM_CLASS_ID FROM PAM_CLASS where EXTERNAL_KEY = p_cl_id);
    
  UPDATE MPULKTM1
    SET PAM_CONFIG_ID_MAIN = v_cn_id
    WHERE TMCODE = v_tmcode
    AND SPCODE = v_spcode
    AND SNCODE = v_sncode;
END;
   BEGIN

 v_date := TO_DATE( '13/05/2015', 'DD/MM/YYYY' );
  v_user := 'SYSADM';
  v_curr := 'MGA';
  
  
  v_sub_gl_acc    :=NULL;
  v_acc_gl_acc    :=NULL;
  v_usg_gl_acc    :=NULL;
  v_sub_cat       :='Standard';
  v_sub_code      :='Standard';
  v_sub_type      :='STD';
  v_acc_cat       :='Exonere2';
  v_acc_code      :='Exonere2';
  v_acc_type      :='STD';
  v_usg_cat       :='Exonere';
  v_usg_code      :='Exonere';
  v_usg_type      :='STD';
